WEBVTT

1
00:14:37.560 --> 00:14:40.930 
比80个足球场还要大
It'll be larger than 80 football fields.

2
00:14:40.930 --> 00:14:42.990 
这是一场豪赌
It's a massive gamble.

3
00:14:43.650 --> 00:14:47.710 
卡内基把全副身家都押在这个新炼钢厂上
Carneg risks everything he's got on the new plant.

4
00:14:48.600 --> 00:14:51.250 
但才建了几个月
But only months into construction...

5
00:14:51.950 --> 00:14:54.080 
灾难降临
disaster.

6
00:14:54.820 --> 00:14:57.860 
股市全面崩溃
A catastrophic stock-market collapse.

7
00:15:00.720 --> 00:15:04.000 
经济大幅衰退
The economy is in free fall.

8
00:15:04.330 --> 00:15:06.870 
他不得不借更多的钱
He has to borrow even more money

9
00:15:06.870 --> 00:15:09.190 
勉强度过难关
and barely scrapes through.

